results.name: Alternating row sums of Riordan triangle A319203.
comment: The row sums are given in A321204.
formula: G.f: f(x)/(1 + x*f(x)) where f(x) = F^([-1])(x)/x with F^{[-1]}(y) the compositional inverse of F(x) = x/(1 - x^2 - x^3). The expansion of f is given in A319201.
